core.login.loginsteps:
Kia ora! Kia whai āheitanga katoa koe ki ō akoranga me waihanga pūkete hōu mōu ki tēnei pae tukutuku. I ia akoranga (takitahi) pea tētehi "kī whakaurunga", engari mō muri kē atu tēnei. Anei ngā hipanga:
  1. Whakakīa te Pūkete hōu puka ki ō taipitopito.
  2. Ka tere tukuna tētehi īmēra ki tō tauwāhi īmēra.
  3. Pānuihia tō īmēra, ā ka pāwhiritia te hononga tukutuku kei roto.
  4. Ka whakaūngia tō pūkete, ā ka takiuru koe.
  5. Ināianei, tīpakohia te akoranga e hiahia whai wāhi nei koe.
  6. Ki te matohitia koe mō tētehi "kī whakaurunga" - whakamahia te mea i hoatu e tō kaiako. Mā tēnei koe hei "whakauru" ki te akoranga.
  7. Ka taea ināianei te uru ki te katoa o te akoranga. Mai ināianei me tāuru i tō ingoa kaiwhakamahi whaiaro me te kupuhipa (i roto i te puka kei tēnei whārangi) kia takiuru me te whai āheitanga ki ngā akoranga kua whakaurua e koe.
